Package org.soulwing.prospecto.api.discriminator

Interface DiscriminatorStrategy

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SimpleClassNameDiscriminatorStrategy, UnqualifiedClassNameDiscriminatorStrategy
    public interface DiscriminatorStrategy
    A strategy that produces a Discriminator for a given model type.

    The strategy consists of a function which is used to transform a type's class into a value that can be composed in a view and the function's inverse, which utilizes a type's discriminator to determine the corresponding class.

    Author:
    Carl Harris
